'''Myneyrsh''' language was the native language of the [[Myneyrsh]] species from [[Wayland/Legends|Wayland]].<ref name="UAA" />

The other intelligent species from Wayland, the [[Psadan]], also used Myneyrsh as a second language. Similarly, most Myneyrsh were fluent in both Myneyrsh and [[Psadan (language)|Psadan]] languages, although they were only literate in their own language. Myneyrsh usually also know to speak [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]].<ref name="UAA" />

Myneyrsh was a primitive language of rough vocalizations, snorts and honks.<ref name="UAA" />

There was no written Myneyrsh, as the Myneyrsh preferred to pass on knowledge orally.<ref name="UAA" />

